  notes:
    - "This spec covers: inspect.signature function qualname and code attributes, plus inspect.Parameter class identity and __init__ code attributes (Wave 262)."
    - "inspect.signature.__qualname__ == 'signature' (len 9) — signature is defined at module scope in Lib/inspect.py. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
